pull_request.body:

Sourced from eslint's releases.

v9.28.0

Features

  • b0674be feat: Customization of serialization for languageOptions (#19760) (Nicholas C. Zakas)
  • a95721f feat: Add --pass-on-unpruned-suppressions CLI option (#19773) (Milos Djermanovic)

Implements comprehensive dashboard analytics with interactive charts and metrics:
- Revenue tracking and rental trend visualization
- Vehicle distribution and status monitoring
- Real-time rental status breakdown

Enhances review management capabilities:
- Centralized review monitoring and moderation
- Rating distribution analytics
- Customer feedback tracking

Improves payment processing interface with detailed transaction history and status tracking.

Charts powered by Chart.js for better data visualization and user experience.
